branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VNB series a 2 port process valve for a wide variety of fluids including air, water, oil, gas and vacuum. It is available with three types of body material: copper alloy, aluminum and stainless steel. 
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;External pilot solenoid type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flow rate ranges from Cv of 0.80 to 43&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orifice size: 7mm to 50mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Port size: 1/8 to 2 Rc(PT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seal material: NBR, FKM, EPR&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

